---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Resources"
  description="Practice schedules, gear guides, and helpful links for skaters and families in the Elmbrook Speedskating program."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="sec-inner page-hero">
      <div class="label">
        <span class="label-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        For skaters &amp; families
      </div>
      <h1 class="heading">Resources</h1>
      <p class="body-text page-lede">
        Practice schedules, gear guides, and helpful links for current and
        prospective skaters. More coming soon.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-inner resources-grid">
      <article class="resource-card">
        <h2 class="resource-title">Speedskating 101</h2>
        <p class="resource-desc">
          New to the sport? US Speedskating's beginner guide covers the
          basics of technique, equipment, and getting started.
        </p>
        <p class="resource-cta">
          <a href="https://www.usspeedskating.org/speedskating-101" rel="noopener" target="_blank">usspeedskating.org →</a>
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <h2 class="resource-title">US Speedskating SafeSport</h2>
        <p class="resource-desc">
          SafeSport training and resources for athletes, parents, and
          coaches to ensure a safe environment for all skaters.
        </p>
        <p class="resource-cta">
          <a href="https://www.usspeedskating.org/safesport" rel="noopener" target="_blank">usspeedskating.org →</a>
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <h2 class="resource-title">US Speedskating Membership</h2>
        <p class="resource-desc">
        Required for regional and national level competitions
          and offers access to resources and events
        </p>
        <p class="resource-cta">
          <a href="https://www.usspeedskating.org/membership" rel="noopener" target="_blank">usspeedskating.org →</a>
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <h2 class="resource-title">FAQ</h2>
        <p class="resource-desc">
          The questions parents ask us most: cost, age range, time
          commitment, safety, and more.
        </p>
        <p class="resource-cta">Coming soon</p>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <h2 class="resource-title">Meets & Competitions</h2>
        <p class="resource-desc">
          Local, state, and national meet calendars and what to expect at your first race.
        </p>
        <p class="resource-cta">
          Coming soon
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <h2 class="resource-title">Elmbrook Speedskating</h2>
        <p class="resource-desc">
          Our partner club site for registration, member accounts, and
          season updates.
        </p>
        <p class="resource-cta">
          <a href="https://www.elmbrookspeedskating.org" rel="noopener">elmbrookspeedskating.org →</a>
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-inner resources-contact">
      <p class="body-text">
        Don't see what you need? Email us at
        <a href="mailto:admin@letsskate.org">admin@letsskate.org</a> and
        we'll point you in the right direction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { text-align: center; padding-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero .label { justify-content: center; }
  .page-hero h1.heading { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
  .page-lede { max-width: 640px; margin: 1rem auto 0; font-size: 1rem; }

  .resources-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .resource-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .resource-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--teal);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,119,139,0.08);
  }
.resource-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  .resource-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .resource-cta {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--teal);
  }
  .resource-cta a { color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; }
  .resource-cta a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .resources-contact {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  .resources-contact a { color: var(--teal); font-weight: 700; }

  @media (max-width: 880px) { .resources-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  @media (max-width: 520px) { .resources-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
